d 'STATA-MCP': Stata MCP — drone, server jar, and ado command suite
d
d Bundles the Stata-side artifacts of the Stata MCP project so they
d can be installed in one shot via `net install stata-mcp, from(...)`
d into the user's PERSONAL ado folder.
d
d Author: mhjung0822
d Support: https://github.com/mhjung0822/stata_mcp-releases
d Distribution-Date: 20260517
d
d Requires: Stata 17 or higher, Java 17+
d
d After install, see INSTALL.md for client (Claude Desktop / Code / Cursor)
d setup and USAGE.md for `mcp_connect` startup.

F stata-mcp-server.jar
F stata-drone.jar
F mcp_connect.ado
F mcp_server.ado
F llm.ado
F graph_meta_put.ado
F mcp_load_serset.ado
